{"parents": [], "prev": null, "next": null, "title": "Events: Managing Campaigns", "meta": {}, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"events-managing-campaigns\">\n<h1>Events: Managing Campaigns<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#events-managing-campaigns\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\"><strong>Campaigns</strong> displays the campaigns associated with an event.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">These campaigns can be sent before (e.g. as a reminder of the time or as a notification of a location change) or after an event (e.g. as a thank you for attending the event).</div>\n<div class=\"line\">To view this feature, you must have navigated to an event. Click <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/events/guides/events/events.html\">here</a> if you are having trouble reaching this point.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-bullhorn\"></i> <strong>Campaigns</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-envelope\"></i> <strong>Email</strong> to view the <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/email/email_campaigns.html\">email campaigns</a> associated with the event</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-comment\"></i> <strong>SMS</strong> to view the <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/outbound_sms/outbound_sms_campaigns.html\">SMS campaigns</a> associated with the event</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-phone\"></i> <strong>Voice</strong> to view the <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/voice/voice_campaigns.html\">voice campaigns</a> associated with the event</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-plus\"></i> to create a new campaign (<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/email/new_email_campaigns.html\">email</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/outbound_sms/new_outbound_sms_campaign.html\">SMS</a> , or <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/voice/new_voice_campaign.html\">voice</a> )</p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"]], "sourcename": "users/events/guides/events/campaigns.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Events: Managing Campaigns</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/events/guides/events/campaigns", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}